name: Intro to Wakesurfing!
description: Welcome to the Zuzalu Wakesurfing Club!! Beginners, intermediate, advanced are all welcome - let's have fun on the water together. We are partnering with https://www.instagram.com/wake_mne/. They will be coming to Zuzalu to do a dry session on the basics of wakesurfing and teach everyone how to get up on the board at your first water session!!!
